       ACTION PERFORMANCE  50%
         Closure Rate          ×30%  — actions closed on time
         Overdue Penalty (inv) ×20%  — fewer overdue = higher score
       ENGAGEMENT             30%
         NCRs Raised           ×15%  — proactive hazard reporting
         Near Miss Reports     ×15%  — safety culture
